'''Jaime''' is the downstairs neighbor of [[Evelyn]].

==History==
When Jaime and his partner [[Liam]], heard creaking in their ceiling and started to see cracks, they worried about their neighbor [[Evelyn]], whose apartment was directly above theirs. They tried calling her, but got no answer, so they called 911. Station 19 responded and found that Evelyn was trapped and her apartment was so full of stuff that it was dangerous to go inside. After Evelyn had been rescued by Andy, Jaime and Liam both told her how glad they were that she was safe, even though her apartment had fallen into theirs.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
He is dating [[Liam]].

===Friendships===
He and Liam are friends with Evelyn, who lived in the apartment above them. She came over to spend time with them and they were worried when she didn't answer her phone.
